Counts and presence/absence of species of macrofauna identified from 14 grab 
samples collected at Allbony Bay Marine Conservation Zone between the 27th 
July and the 8 <sup>...</sup> September 2014.

The data were collected for the Marine Conversation Zones Project funded by 
the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs (DEFRA).
